title: 3DSimED3.with.Trial.Reset.v1
description:
_____________________________________________________________

3DSimED 3.0 Trial Reset Tool. - V1.0 FINAL - ## 21/08/2014 ##
_____________________________________________________________

INSTALL:

1.) Copy Launcher.exe to 3DSimED's root directory (the same folder as 3DSimED3.exe)


USEAGE:

1.) Use Launcher.exe to start the program instead of 3DSimED3.exe. Each time the program loads the trial is reset to 20 days. It's crude, but I have no idea how to unpack PC Guard 5.0......yet ;)


-ASBO
